------------------------------------------------------------------------

- ask if an existing file will be overwritten or skipped
- option to force overwriting of all files
- option to strip directories from filenames
- option to create directory tree in filenames
- handle invalid filenames (create alternative filename or ask for one?)
- possibility to extract only files matching wildcard arguments
  (e.g. "uncfl file.cfl *.foo bar*")
- option to simulate what will be happen without actually writing files
- option to delete all files from disk listed in the cfl file
- option to print the software license
